{"tid":1382473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大家都話罷工】有少少野想同大家講","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T23:49:53.000Z","uid":94327,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c51bc1f33f4a7d0cdaa22aef8d9cc7b55d954208","tid":1382473,"uid":94327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"運動發展到呢到，好多謝有大家同行。未來呢一個星期，都有唔少手足幫手捲動到佢嘅行業/職場嘅打工仔出嚟罷工。<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港無發生過政治性嘅罷工，多數都係就住人工同待遇問題發起罷工行動；其實香港嘅勞工法例真係落後到仆街，對罷工嘅保障少至又少。不過大家都可以了解下一啲罷工須知。我見職工盟嘅 facebook係有一個詳細嘅罷工須知可以參考下。<br />\n<br />\n除此以外，我地都見到要組織起職場/行業嘅打工仔，其實都要想對應嘅時間，同時，如過有手足想<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搞工會</span></span>，呢到都有個懶人包話下成個程序，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲可以計劃下入埋勞工界別，唔好畀建制派霸鳩住，騎劫業界聲音。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gwyc7xK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgwyc7xK.jpg&h=be5f8686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqkGgq4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqkGgq4.png&h=525a959d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0CENxL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0CENxL.png&h=a0cb3be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHeS7xL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHeS7xL.png&h=feaff138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWiHLjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWiHLjr.png&h=011f92b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求！缺一不可，大家要撐住！齊上齊落堅持到底！</span></span><br />\n另外，如果就真開始feel到自己公司有同事都係隱性手足，要諗下計點樣集合返所有人，壯大喺職場嘅力量，呢股力量係要有持續性，當政府有咩仆街野，或者重大事件發生，就可以立即作出反應發動罷工，就靠大家拋磚引肉了！"},{"pid":"a74c3264a93b64b01c62e73ce9911ace9a1c117e","tid":1382473,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1f3967fc0dd5d2013e1b2abf48745a8daa4e439e","tid":1382473,"uid":11937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"「全港大罷工」動搖唔到經濟民生佔晒全香港都無用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsovuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsovuS</a>"},{"pid":"712f37490dcf2ad9031d31ab9e71592c0e4bcbeb","tid":1382473,"uid":127331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e845dce46956575c8cb47362e57db51317c1ffc","tid":1382473,"uid":94327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"罷工須知：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/strikeforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctu.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2FstrikeforHK&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=fee5ba1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/strikeforHK</a><br />\n<br />\n想發起「政治性罷工」要考慮什麼問題？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/120514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F120514&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=68ac34ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/120514</a><br />\n<br />\n搞工會，反送中channel：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/unionsforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FunionsforHK&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=4b29edaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/unionsforHK</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/ru